FBIS4-41318 "drsov122_a_94023" FBIS-SOV-94-122 Daily Report 23 Jun 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Prime Minister Chernomyrdin Continues U.S. Visit Prime Minister Chernomyrdin Continues U.S. Visit Comments on Trade Restrictions LD2306123094 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1200 GMT 23 Jun 94 LD2306123094 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Russian BFN [Text] Russian Prime Minister Viktor Chernomyrdin, who is in the USA, said that he had succeeded in persuading the American administration that it is necessary to acknowledge Russia as a country whose economy is in a state of transition. According to Chernomyrdin, U.S. leaders favor the lifting of unjustified restrictions on trade with Russia.
